-- A2A May Sell Selene, Metroweb Stakes to Cut Debt
-- B y   T o m m a s o   E b h a r d t
-- 2012-09-30T09:58:22Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-09-30/a2a-may-sell-selene-metroweb-stakes-to-cut-debt.html
The Italian utility wants to exit
the telecommunications business, selling its 25.7% stake in
Metroweb and majority stake in Selene, Il Sole 24 Ore reports,
without citing anyone.
* A2A may get 60 million euros ($77 million) from the sale of
